David Shapiro from Sasfin Securities chose Microsoft as his stock pick of the day and Wayne McCurrie from FNB Wealth & Investments chose cash. Shapiro said: “I looked at Microsoft’s results and they are pretty good, I think we’re going to get similar results from all the tech companies. I looked at the gaming side and the cloud side of Microsoft and I still think these are massive themes that are going to dominate.” McCurrie said: “I’m going to be a bit more cautious and I’m going to sit on cash. I think there could be a little bit of weakness coming into the market.” Or listen to the full audio: Subscribe for free episodes: iono.fm | Spotify | Pocket Casts | Player.fm